  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813;font-size:13px\">This is an optional class feature. Consult with your DM before adding this to your character.</em></p>\n<p>Also at 3rd level, you can expend a use of your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.BdhVFmTGhjLm1Ceo]{Channel Divinity} to fuel your spells. As a bonus action, you touch your holy symbol, utter a prayer, and regain <strong>one expended spell slot</strong>, the level of which can be no higher than <strong>half your proficiency bonus</strong> (rounded up). The number of times you can use this feature is based on the level you've reached in this class: 3rd level, once; 7th level, twice; and 15th level, thrice. You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: When you add this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Channel Divinity.</em></p>\n</section>",
